      <title>加拿大股市上涨 22% 后，Ned Davis 将评级上调至增持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/canada-stocks-upgraded-to-overweight-by-ned-davis-after-22-jump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大股市的上涨促使 Ned Davis Research 敦促投资者通过将多伦多上市股票的评级上调至增持来增加对市场的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/canada-stocks-upgraded-to-overweight-by-ned-davis-after-22-jump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 14:30:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>集团首席财务官表示，阿达尼绿色美元债券可能在 2025 年中期恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/adani-green-dollar-bond-may-be-revived-mid-2025-group-cfo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[集团首席财务官 Jugeshinder Singh 周五表示，阿达尼绿色能源有限公司 (Adani Green Energy Ltd.) 将考虑在 4 月至 6 月期间重新发行已废除的美元债券，此举彰显了尽管美国对创始人 Gautam Adani 展开调查，该集团仍具有强大的韧性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/adani-green-dollar-bond-may-be-revived-mid-2025-group-cfo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 14:25:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西资产将因预算计划遭遇两年来最糟糕的一周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/brazil-markets-set-for-worst-week-in-two-years-on-spending-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西股市有望迎来两年来最糟糕的一周，此前备受吹捧的削减政府开支计划令投资者感到失望，并加剧了人们对该国预算的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/brazil-markets-set-for-worst-week-in-two-years-on-spending-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 13:10:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
