      <title>阿拉比卡咖啡因供应担忧有望创 2014 年以来最大月度涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/arabica-set-for-largest-monthly-gain-since-2014-on-supply-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉比卡咖啡期货有望创下十多年来的最大月度涨幅，涨势受到全球供应担忧和对出口商将面临财务压力的担忧推动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/arabica-set-for-largest-monthly-gain-since-2014-on-supply-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 12:31:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合信贷银行将与法国农业信贷银行讨论 Amundi 协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/unicredit-plans-to-meet-credit-agricole-to-discuss-banco-bpm-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[未来几周，意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 和法国农业信贷银行 (Credit Agricole SA) 的高管将齐聚一堂，讨论意大利联合信贷银行收购国内竞争对手一事，届时两家公司之间还将讨论一项至关重要的分销协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/unicredit-plans-to-meet-credit-agricole-to-discuss-banco-bpm-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 09:40:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>很少有人预料到，这是美国股市丰收的一年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/the-vintage-year-for-us-stock-markets-that-few-people-expected</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一年前，股票投资者和策略师们为可能动荡的2024年做好了准备，担心美国经济硬着陆的风险，以及可能来不及阻止这种情况的降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/the-vintage-year-for-us-stock-markets-that-few-people-expected</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 08:09:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
